cdata.name: Everus
cdata.desc:
Everus (EVR) is aplatform that will leveragethe Ethereum blockchain to empower their services. Services like an exchange, its own cryptocurrency ATM, a BaaS (Blockchain as a Service) enabling decentralizedapplications to use it as a payment service, and an e-Mall (EVR Mall).

EVR is an ERC-20 token that will provide users with voting rights
